data.description: Welcome to your charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom retreat at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. This renovated home sits on a spacious 1/5-acre lot, offering you plenty of privacy. As you step inside, you'll find a spacious open-concept living and dining area, perfect for gatherings. The kitchen has been tastefully remodeled and features a cozy breakfast nook - a great space for cooking and enjoying meals. The nice size master bedroom offers two closets and an updated bathroom. On the other side of the home, you'll discover two roomy spare bedrooms, ideal for family or guests, and they share a well-maintained hall bathroom. Outside, you'll love the new back porch and the covered front porch - perfect spots for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors.
